pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `administrator` ( `Eatery_ID` int(11) NOT NULL, `User_ID` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `Permission_Level` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Eatery_ID`,`User_ID`), KEY `User_ID` (`User_ID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `eatery` ( `Eatery_ID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Eatery_Name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Website` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci DEFAULT NULL, `Start_Hour` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `End_Hour` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `Open_Days` varchar(24) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci DEFAULT NULL, `Address` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Pricing` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `Coordinates` point DEFAULT NULL, `Phone_Num` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `Regional_Type` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Eatery_Type` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Cuisine` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Eatery_ID`), UNIQUE KEY `Eatery_ID` (`Eatery_ID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `eateryvisit` ( `User_ID` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `Eatery_ID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Visit_Date` datetime NOT NULL, `Feedback` varchar(255) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Eatery_ID`,`User_ID`,`Visit_Date`), KEY `User_ID` (`User_ID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `menu` ( `Eatery_ID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Menu_ID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Start_Hour` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `End_Hour` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `Menu_Type` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Eatery_ID`,`Menu_ID`), KEY `Eatery_ID` (`Eatery_ID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `menu_item` ( `Eatery_ID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Menu_ID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Item_ID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Item_Type` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Item_Name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Item_Price` double DEFAULT NULL, `Item_Description` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Eatery_ID`,`Menu_ID`,`Item_ID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `preference` ( `User_ID` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `Item_Type` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `Count_Visited` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `Rating` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`User_ID`,`Item_Type`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `tempsearch` ( `Eatery_ID` int(11) NOT NULL, `Eatery_Name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Website` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci DEFAULT NULL, `Start_Hour` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `End_Hour` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `Open_Days` varchar(24) DEFAULT NULL, `Address` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Pricing` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `Coordinates` point DEFAULT NULL, `Phone_Num` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `Regional_Type` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Eatery_Type` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Cuisine` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Eatery_ID`), UNIQUE KEY `Eatery_ID` (`Eatery_ID`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `usertable` ( `User_ID` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `Display_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `Address` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `Total_Outings` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`User_ID`), UNIQUE KEY `User_ID` (`User_ID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;
pma:database.pma:procedure: CREATE DEFINER=`atakan`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `Preference`(IN `User_ID_in` VARCHAR(100)) NO SQL INSERT INTO preference (User_ID, Item_Type, Count_Visited, Rating) (SELECT User_ID_in AS User_ID, Item_Type, COUNT(Item_Type) AS ItemCount, 0 FROM tempsearch NATURAL JOIN menu_item GROUP BY Item_Type ORDER BY ItemCount DESC LIMIT 5) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE Count_Visited = Count_Visited + 1
